<h2 id="head-70440046a3dc2e079f23ee1c57dfa76669b732aa">Notes</h2>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 The ability to pass a record selector as a first-class function value is key to the succinctness of this technique. 
</p>
</li>
</ul>

